    "description": "Color Pals is a cute platformer puzzle game consisting of 50 levels where your objective is to get to the exit matching the correct colors along the way. Be careful, touching a block that doesn't match your color or hitting an enemy, kills you instantly.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanics</h2><br>You can only touch blocks, keys, and the exit that match your current color. Collect colored bolts to change colors and grab keys to open pathways!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/3430151540b1361bf31e1f9afb13de00.poster.avif?t=1685615417\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/3430151540b1361bf31e1f9afb13de00.webm?t=1685615417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/3430151540b1361bf31e1f9afb13de00.mp4?t=1685615417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stars</h2><br>Every level has 3 stars placed throughout. See if you can collect them all! Track all the Stars you've collected and see how many you can get!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/a350f3d0ce863175b3beb17888927f03.poster.avif?t=1685615417\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/a350f3d0ce863175b3beb17888927f03.webm?t=1685615417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/a350f3d0ce863175b3beb17888927f03.mp4?t=1685615417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2><br>Watch out for the spiked enemies as they will love to kill you at any moment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/58a493f1ee1c8c31699072a3d37f74d7.poster.avif?t=1685615417\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/58a493f1ee1c8c31699072a3d37f74d7.webm?t=1685615417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141780/extras/58a493f1ee1c8c31699072a3d37f74d7.mp4?t=1685615417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
